觀光業是[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]經濟的重要產業，其產值佔紐西蘭GDP的3.7%，並且產生了110,800的就業崗位，佔紐西蘭總就業人口的6%<ref>http://www.med.govt.nz/sectors-industries/tourism/pdf-docs-library/key-tourism-statistics/key-tourism-statistics.pdf</ref>。現任紐西蘭總理[[約翰·基|約翰·基]]也同時兼任觀光部長<ref name="nyt20121124">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/11/24/business/media/new-zealand-wants-a-hollywood-put-on-its-map.html | title=New Zealand Wants a Hollywood Put on Its Map | work=The New York Times | date=2012-11-24 | accessdate=6 April 2014 | author=Cieply, Michael; Barnes, Brooke | pages=A1}}</ref>。紐西蘭以其清潔綠色的環境作為主要觀光的賣點。2012年，紐西蘭被英國報紙[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]選為假日最佳度假國家<ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.3news.co.nz/NZ-tops-UK-holiday-poll/tabid/421/articleID/276927/Default.aspx| work= 3 News NZ| title= NZ tops UK holiday poll| date= 16 November 2012| access-date= 2016-02-02| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130415150027/http://www.3news.co.nz/NZ-tops-UK-holiday-poll/tabid/421/articleID/276927/Default.aspx| archive-date= 2013-04-15| dead-url= yes}}</ref>。絕大多數外國遊客在[[奧克蘭機場|奧克蘭機場]]抵達紐西蘭，2013年佔總數的近15%。另外有2%通過坐船到達紐西蘭（2009年）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.med.govt.nz/sectors-industries/tourism/pdf-docs-library/tourism-research-and-data/other-research-and-reports/tourism-sector-profiles/international-visitor-markets/total-profile.pdf |title=International visitors: total |date=June 2009 |publisher=Ministry of Tourism |accessdate=7 June 2015 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。紐西蘭最大的10個外國遊客客源如下<ref>[http://www.immigration.govt.nz/migrant/general/generalinformation/statistics/ Immigration New Zealand statistics - A1b - Arrivals by month]</ref>：

